le=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"dark\" custom_css_blurb_title=\"color: #b92025;\"]\n\n FRC(functional range conditioning) Certified\n Certified Personal Trainer (ACE, NASM)\n Poliquin Biosignature Practitioner, Level 2\n Sports Performance Coach (USAW)\n Nutrition and Lifestyle Coach (Chek Institute)\n Certified Massage Therapist w/advanced training (LifeStream Massage School, Napa, CA)\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Erick Minor\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_layout=\"dark\"]\n\n<h2>Erick Minor</h2>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"FOUNDER & CEO, STRENGTH STUDIO INC.\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"redtxt\"]\n\n<h4>FOUNDER &amp; CEO, STRENGTH STUDIO INC.</h4>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Erick Minor Bio\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_layout=\"dark\"]\n\nPersonal trainer and strength coach, Erick Minor, is a leading expert in the fields of athletic preparation, muscle hypertrophy, and fat loss. Erick became interested in exercise at the age of 18 when he enlisted in the U.S. Air Force. HIs love of strength training led him to compete in powerlifting, bodybuilding, and strongman. His experience as an athlete and coach has enhanced his ability to achieve optimal results for his clients.\n\nErick has mastered the art of designing strength programs and nutritional strategies that ensure rapid results. This integrated approach allows his clients to lose fat, gain muscle, reduce injury potential, and improve athletic performance in a safe and efficient manner. Along with training many fitness enthusiasts and physique athletes, Erick has trained collegiate, Olympic and professional athletes from several sports including; track and field, MLB, MMA, football, and golf.\n\nWith over 22 years of practical experience in strength training, and an extensive background in kinesiology, nutrition, and supplementation; Erick is recognized as an innovator in the fitness industry.\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"How it Works\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_layout=\"light\"]\n\n<h1>How It Works</h1>\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_color=\"#ededed\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Trainer\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_layout=\"light\"]\n\n<h4>TRAINER</h4>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_video _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" src=\"https://youtu.be/q6k_B_pDyXU\" image_src=\"//i.ytimg.com/vi/q6k_B_pDyXU/hqdefault.jpg\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Gym\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_layout=\"light\"]\n\n<h4>GYM</h4>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_video _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" src=\"https://youtu.be/q6k_B_pDyXU\" image_src=\"http://sm.ampluswebsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/erick_minor_vid.jpg\" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Pricing\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_layout=\"light\"]\n\n<h1>Pricing</h1>\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_pricing_tables _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'Strength Metrix', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-02-19 23:36:51', '2018-02-19 23:36:51', '', 2, 'http://sm.ampluswebsites.com/uncategorized/2-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
