 safe and efficient manner. Along with training many fitness enthusiasts and physique athletes, Erick has trained collegiate, Olympic and professional athletes from several sports including; track and field, MLB, MMA, football, and golf. With over 22 years of practical experience in strength training, and an extensive background in kinesiology, nutrition, and supplementation; Erick is recognized as an innovator in the fitness industry.\r[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row background_color=\"#c7c7c7\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Certifications\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" header_font=\"Montserrat|700|||||||\" header_text_align=\"center\" header_font_size=\"24px\" header_text_color=\"#ae1f23\"]<h1>Certifications</h1>\r[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row background_color=\"#c7c7c7\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" custom_css_main_element=\"padding: 10px 100px 25px 100px !important;\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_text background_layout=\"dark\" admin_label=\"Certified Personal Trainer (ACE, NASM)\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" text_font=\"Montserrat|700||on|||||\" text_font_size=\"16px\" text_line_height=\"1.2em\" header_font=\"Montserrat|700|||||||\" header_text_align=\"center\" header_font_size=\"24px\" header_text_color=\"#ae1f23\" background_color=\"#323232\" text_orientation=\"center\" custom_padding=\"10px||10px|\"]Certified Personal Trainer (ACE, NASM)\r[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text background_layout=\"dark\" admin_label=\"Poliquin Biosignature Practitioner Level 2\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" text_font=\"Montserrat|700||on|||||\" text_font_size=\"16px\" text_line_heigh